  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="index.html">Home</a> / Industries</div>
      <h1>Built for the Sectors We Understand</h1>
      <p>Every industry runs on different workflows, compliance needs, and daily pressure points. We design around yours instead of forcing a generic system on top of it.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card anim">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-school"></i></div>
          <h3>Education</h3>
          <p>School ERP systems covering fees, portals, attendance, timetabling, and M-Pesa collection - already running live for 1,000+ students.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card anim">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-hospital"></i></div>
          <h3>Healthcare</h3>
          <p>Patient records, appointment scheduling, and administrative systems built with the data sensitivity healthcare requires.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card anim">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-seedling"></i></div>
          <h3>Agriculture</h3>
          <p>Order and catalogue systems for farms and agribusinesses - proven with 700+ customers on a live poultry ordering platform.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card anim">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-store"></i></div>
          <h3>Retail</h3>
          <p>Inventory, point-of-sale, and e-commerce systems that keep stock counts and sales records accurate in real time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card anim">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-hotel"></i></div>
          <h3>Hospitality</h3>
          <p>Booking, rental, and guest management systems for hotels and hospitality businesses.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card anim">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i></div>
          <h3>Professional Services</h3>
          <p>Client management, quotation, and invoicing tools - like our own Adalyn Sales platform, built for service-based businesses.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card anim">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart"></i></div>
          <h3>NGOs</h3>
          <p>Program tracking, reporting, and donor management systems that hold up to funder scrutiny.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card anim">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-university"></i></div>
          <h3>Financial Services</h3>
          <p>SACCO and finance management systems with the reconciliation and audit trail requirements the sector demands.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card anim">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-landmark"></i></div>
          <h3>Government & Public Sector</h3>
          <p>Structured record-keeping and reporting systems built for accountability and long-term maintainability.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card anim">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-truck"></i></div>
          <h3>Logistics</h3>
          <p>Fleet and GPS tracking systems that give operations teams visibility into vehicles and deliveries in real time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

